title: Tuts Tomb 4.03 Slot Machine Pokie [Egyptian Themed] *FULL*
description:
Tuts Tomb is a 5 reel, 243 payline aussie style slot machine (pokie) with
a egyptian based theme. Play 1, 3, 9, 27, 81, or 243 PaylinesWin the
Feature whenever 3 or more scattered appear. Win the Major Jackpot
whenever 5 scattered appear during the feature . Ability to double up
wins. New features included in the new version of Tuts Tomb. Bill
acceptor, Reserved Button, Scrollable Paytable, and added sound option in
